          <p><a href="https://github.com/blog/1375-task-lists-in-gfm-issues-pulls-comments">Task lists</a> in issues, comments, and pull request descriptions are incredibly useful for project coordination and keeping track of important items. Starting today, we are adding read-only task lists to all Markdown documents in repositories and wikis. So now, when you write:</p>\
